#  7.  6 
from itertools import combinations

fig = plt.figure(figsize = (12, 8))
index = 0

for comb in list(combinations(person_features, 2)):
    xdata = sdata[comb[0]]
    ydata = sdata[comb[1]]
    
    ax = fig.add_subplot(2, 3, index+1)
    ax.scatter(xdata[labels==1], ydata[labels==1], c='blue', alpha=0.3, label='1')
    ax.scatter(xdata[labels==-1], ydata[labels==-1], c='red', alpha=0.3, label='-1')
    ax.set_xlabel(comb[0])
    ax.set_ylabel(comb[1])
    index += 1
